The paper deals with object recognition in images using natural language queries and dialogs, which is a problem in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of natural language also suggests a connection to natural language processing (cs.CL). The proposed framework involves attention mechanisms and reasoning, which are common techniques in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper also mentions benchmarked datasets, which suggests an evaluation aspect that could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR).
